thread.title: BRIEF-Tatwah Smartech signs strategic cooperation agreement with internet tech firm

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Tatwah Smartech signs strategic cooperation agreement with internet tech firm
text:
Jan 18 (Reuters) - Tatwah Smartech Co Ltd :
* Says it signed a strategic cooperation agreement with an internet tech company, the largest VSAT facility provider in the world, regarding satellite communication commercial operation service, the satellite communication market development and space information intercommunication
